The first one was wonderful.

17:13.642 --> 17:17.086
Not well written.

17:17.106 --> 17:17.507
It was awful.

17:17.567 --> 17:20.470
But the second one, I felt the second one was better written.

17:21.312 --> 17:22.453
But this time...

17:22.788 --> 17:33.588
