I mean, the people in Maine.

30:28.063 --> 30:29.605
I mean, there were some people in some areas who said, you know,

30:30.563 --> 30:38.374
Yeah, George Mitchell didn't want me to tell him.

30:38.394 --> 30:38.775
Is that right?

30:38.955 --> 30:40.658
He said, what do they think of us?

30:40.738 --> 30:45.244
He wanted everybody to think that we were all like him and George Bush.

30:47.387 --> 30:51.954
And the yellow-ringed coat guy with a little smile on the pipe.

30:52.034 --> 30:58.984
But besides him, there were a lot of people who were very close to having any income, at the time, having no income.

30:59.386 --> 31:05.219
who kind of, I think they were afraid that people would say well like that, because they were so close, you know what I mean?

